main event: A UFO sighting report from March 15, 1965, involving an unidentified object photographed near the Plain of Jars, Laos.
interesting points: The observer used a 35mm camera to capture images of the unidentified object., The images were taken from a C-46 aircraft., A detailed analysis could not confirm the object's identity due to poor image quality., The report includes correspondence with various officials regarding the object's analysis., The object appeared to have some draping material obscuring part of it in the photographs.
witness description: Capt. [redacted] reported seeing the object and submitted his photographic evidence.
